# Check Your Drawings — environment variables

## Backend (Render)

```env
AUTH_REQUIRED=false
ANONYMOUS_ALLOWANCE_TOTAL=5
# Throughput — active jobs only (pending + running); do not add daily caps or tiered file sizes
MAX_ANON_ACTIVE_JOBS=1
MAX_FREE_ACTIVE_JOBS=1
MAX_PRO_ACTIVE_JOBS=10
CORS_ORIGINS=https://checkyourdrawings.kvshvl.in,http://localhost:5173
PLATFORM_DATABASE_URL=postgresql://...
PLATFORM_API_URL=https://platform-api.kvshvl.in
PLATFORM_JWT_SECRET=
PLATFORM_JWT_ISSUER=https://platform-auth.kvshvl.in
OUTPUT_MAX_AGE_HOURS=24
COMPARE_DEBUG=false
COMPARE_MAX_RASTER_PIXELS=8000000
MIN_INK_PIXEL_RATIO=0.001
OVERLAY_AGREE_DILATION_RADIUS=3
BUNNY_STORAGE_ZONE=kvshvl-platform
BUNNY_STORAGE_ACCESS_KEY=
BUNNY_STORAGE_REGION=ny
BUNNY_STORAGE_PREFIX=checkyourdrawings
BUNNY_CDN_HOSTNAME=kvshvl-platform-cdn.b-cdn.net
BUNNY_TOKEN_AUTH_KEY=
BUNNY_SIGNED_URL_TTL_SECONDS=86400
```

## Frontend (Vercel)

```env
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://checkyourdrawings-api.kvshvl.in
VITE_PLATFORM_API_URL=https://platform-api.kvshvl.in
VITE_KVSHVL_AUTH_URL=https://platform-auth.kvshvl.in
VITE_BUNNY_CDN_HOSTNAME=kvshvl-platform-cdn.b-cdn.net
```

Copy secrets into `.env.deploy.local` (gitignored) for `scripts/deploy_render_env.py`.
